#: applications/luci-app-aurora-config/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/aurora/theme.js:458
msgid "Semantic & Status Colors"
msgstr "Warna Semantik & Status"

#: applications/luci-app-aurora-config/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/aurora/theme.js:460
msgid ""
"Semantic colors represent different actions and intents, commonly used in "
"buttons and badges. For example, destructive (Destructive) maps to high‑risk "
"actions like delete or reset. Status colors represent system feedback "
"states, commonly used in tooltip messages (Tooltip), alert dialogs (Alert), "
"status tags (Tag), and legends (Legend). Each status type (Default, Info, "
"Warning, Success, Error) has two colors: a background color and a foreground/"
"text color (Foreground)."
msgstr "Warna semantik mewakili berbagai tindakan dan maksud, umumnya digunakan pada tombol dan lencana. Sebagai contoh, destruktif (Destructive) dipetakan ke tindakan berisiko tinggi seperti hapus atau atur ulang. Warna status mewakili keadaan umpan balik sistem, umumnya digunakan dalam pesan petunjuk alat (Tooltip), dialog peringatan (Alert), tag status (Tag), dan legenda (Legend). Setiap jenis status (Bawaan, Info, Peringatan, Sukses, Galat) memiliki dua warna: warna latar belakang dan warna latar depan/teks (Foreground)."

