#: applications/luci-app-aurora-config/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/aurora/theme.js:444
msgid ""
"The theme layout uses three layers: background (Background) → page container "
"(Page) → panel card (Panel). The Base Colors variables define each layer's "
"background color (Background) and foreground/text color (Foreground). The "
"primary color (Primary) is mainly used for focused/active states of inputs, "
"selects, radios, checkboxes, and dropdowns, and is also used for key buttons "
"and the page footer."
msgstr "Tata letak tema menggunakan tiga lapisan: latar belakang makro (Background) → kontainer halaman (Page) → kartu panel (Panel). Variabel Warna Dasar menentukan warna latar belakang (Background) dan warna latar depan/teks (Foreground) untuk setiap lapisan. Warna utama (Primary) digunakan terutama untuk status terfokus/aktif pada bidang input, menu pilihan, tombol radio, kotak centang, dan menu turun, serta digunakan untuk tombol-tombol penting dan bagian kaki halaman (footer)."

